                                >סַוְוּלוּגוּמֶנְמו֗</foreign>
                            ; a scribal error.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Kings2-008-fn2" type="footnote">TKow.02: the phrase <emph>ki
                                qyzy Aḥʾavnyn</emph> was mistakenly written twice.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Kings2-008-fn3" type="footnote">TKow.02: spelled <foreign
